        <item>_________ Depending on different seasons, restaurant menus may present a variety of dessert.</item>
        <item>_________ Menu items are often numbered only when the restaurant has a cash register.</item>
        <item>_________ The communication problem with menu numbering is that customers order foods and drinks while the waiter/waitress has to note down the number.</item>
